name: 丹尼尔·瑞安·阿斯特利
name_full: 丹尼尔·瑞安·阿斯特利 Daniel Ryan-Astley
introduction: Daniel Ryan-Astley is a Canadian Actor & Singer who is known for their bubbly and energetic personality. They were born June 02 2001 and grew up in Brantford Ontario, participating in the arts. Some of their most memorable performances have been in community theatre productions within Brantford Ontario. In 2020, Daniel began to release music into the world. Thus starting their ambitions to go out and share their love of the arts with the world.
